<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Approved</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
        .button { background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .success-box { background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #10b981; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 Account Approved!</h1>
            <h2>Welcome to IGL AMC Dashboard</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Congratulations {{userName}}!</h3>
            <p>Your <strong>{{userRole}}</strong> account has been approved by the administrator.</p>
            
            <div class="success-box">
                <h4>✅ Your Account Details</h4>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                    <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{userName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{userRole}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Employee ID:</strong> {{empId}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold;">ACTIVE</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>🚀 What You Can Do Now:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ <strong>Login to Dashboard:</strong> Access your personalized dashboard</li>
                <li>✅ <strong>Manage Contracts:</strong> View and manage AMC contracts</li>
                <li>✅ <strong>Generate Reports:</strong> Create professional reports</li>
                <li>✅ <strong>Track Performance:</strong> Monitor contract performance metrics</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team for any assistance.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 IGL AMC Dashboard. Professional Contract Management.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
